  /*
  ---INFO---
  some people like to post fics with no summary and no freeform tags
  if they can't be bothered, neither can i tbh
  so this skin blocks them
  if they come back later and update it with a summary, it'll be unblocked automatically
  i still won't see it bc it's in the past but that's also not my problem
  */
.blurb:has(ul.required-tags):not(:has(.freeforms > .tag)):not(:has(blockquote)) {
  display: none !important;
}
